{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.1","label":"","reference":"Apocalypse 4:1","prev_osis_id":"Rev.003.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rev.004.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le tr\u00f4ne de la majest\u00e9 divine, les vingt-quatre vieillards, et les quatre \u00eatres vivants<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-11: cf. \u00c9s 6:1-3. \u00c9z 1.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rev.4.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s cela, je regardai, et voici, une porte \u00e9tait ouverte dans le ciel. La premi\u00e8re voix que j\u2019avais entendue, comme le son d\u2019une trompette, et qui me parlait, dit: <span class=\"wj\">Monte ici, et je te ferai voir ce qui doit arriver dans la suite.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rev.4","name":"Apocalypse 4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.2","name":"Apocalypse 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.3.22","name":"Apocalypse 3:22","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.3.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.2","label":"","reference":"Apocalypse 4:2","prev_osis_id":"Rev.004.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rev.004.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rev.4.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Aussit\u00f4t je fus ravi en esprit. Et voici, il y avait un tr\u00f4ne dans le ciel, et sur ce tr\u00f4ne quelqu\u2019un \u00e9tait assis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rev.4","name":"Apocalypse 4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.3","name":"Apocalypse 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.1","name":"Apocalypse 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.3","label":"","reference":"Apocalypse 4:3","prev_osis_id":"Rev.004.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rev.004.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rev.4.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Celui qui \u00e9tait assis avait l\u2019aspect d\u2019une pierre de jaspe et de sardoine; et le tr\u00f4ne \u00e9tait environn\u00e9 d\u2019un arc-en-ciel semblable \u00e0 de l\u2019\u00e9meraude.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rev.4","name":"Apocalypse 4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.4","name":"Apocalypse 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.2","name":"Apocalypse 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.4","label":"","reference":"Apocalypse 4:4","prev_osis_id":"Rev.004.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rev.004.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rev.4.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Autour du tr\u00f4ne je vis vingt-quatre tr\u00f4nes, et sur ces tr\u00f4nes vingt-quatre vieillards assis, rev\u00eatus de v\u00eatements blancs, et sur leurs t\u00eates des couronnes d\u2019or.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rev.4","name":"Apocalypse 4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.5","name":"Apocalypse 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.3","name":"Apocalypse 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.5","label":"","reference":"Apocalypse 4:5","prev_osis_id":"Rev.004.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rev.004.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rev.4.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Du tr\u00f4ne sortent des \u00e9clairs, des voix et des tonnerres. Devant le tr\u00f4ne br\u00fblent sept lampes ardentes, qui sont les sept esprits de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rev.4","name":"Apocalypse 4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.6","name":"Apocalypse 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.4","name":"Apocalypse 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.6","label":"","reference":"Apocalypse 4:6","prev_osis_id":"Rev.004.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rev.004.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rev.4.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il y a encore devant le tr\u00f4ne comme une mer de verre, semblable \u00e0 du cristal. Au milieu du tr\u00f4ne et autour du tr\u00f4ne, il y a quatre \u00eatres vivants remplis d\u2019yeux devant et derri\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rev.4","name":"Apocalypse 4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.7","name":"Apocalypse 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.5","name":"Apocalypse 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.7","label":"","reference":"Apocalypse 4:7","prev_osis_id":"Rev.004.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rev.004.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rev.4.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Le premier \u00eatre vivant est semblable \u00e0 un lion, le second \u00eatre vivant est semblable \u00e0 un veau, le troisi\u00e8me \u00eatre vivant a la face d\u2019un homme, et le quatri\u00e8me \u00eatre vivant est semblable \u00e0 un aigle qui vole.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rev.4","name":"Apocalypse 4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.8","name":"Apocalypse 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.6","name":"Apocalypse 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.8","label":"","reference":"Apocalypse 4:8","prev_osis_id":"Rev.004.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rev.004.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rev.4.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Les quatre \u00eatres vivants ont chacun six ailes, et ils sont remplis d\u2019yeux tout autour et au-dedans. Ils ne cessent de dire jour et nuit: Saint, saint, saint est le Seigneur Dieu, le Tout-Puissant, qui \u00e9tait, qui est, et qui vient!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rev.4","name":"Apocalypse 4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.9","name":"Apocalypse 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.7","name":"Apocalypse 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.9","label":"","reference":"Apocalypse 4:9","prev_osis_id":"Rev.004.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rev.004.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rev.4.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Quand les \u00eatres vivants rendent gloire et honneur et actions de gr\u00e2ces \u00e0 celui qui est assis sur le tr\u00f4ne, \u00e0 celui qui vit aux si\u00e8cles des si\u00e8cles,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rev.4","name":"Apocalypse 4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.10","name":"Apocalypse 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.8","name":"Apocalypse 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.10","label":"","reference":"Apocalypse 4:10","prev_osis_id":"Rev.004.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rev.004.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rev.4.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>les vingt-quatre vieillards se prosternent devant celui qui est assis sur le tr\u00f4ne, et ils adorent celui qui vit aux si\u00e8cles des si\u00e8cles, et ils jettent leurs couronnes devant le tr\u00f4ne, en disant:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rev.4","name":"Apocalypse 4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.11","name":"Apocalypse 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.9","name":"Apocalypse 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.11","label":"","reference":"Apocalypse 4:11","prev_osis_id":"Rev.004.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rev.005.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rev.4.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Tu es digne, notre Seigneur et notre Dieu, de recevoir la gloire et l\u2019honneur et la puissance; car tu as cr\u00e9\u00e9 toutes choses, et c\u2019est par ta volont\u00e9 qu\u2019elles existent et qu\u2019elles ont \u00e9t\u00e9 cr\u00e9\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rev.4","name":"Apocalypse 4","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.5.1","name":"Apocalypse 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.5.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rev.4.10","name":"Apocalypse 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Rev.4.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb61433a6.60234833');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb61433a6.60234833\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb61433a6.60234833","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typ